**************************************************************************
To start using Zelta, you will need to configure the conf file located at:

    /usr/local/etc/zelta/zelta.conf

For detailed information on configuring Zelta, please refer to the documentation:

    https://github.com/bellhyve/zelta/blob/main/README.md

If you find any bugs please file them @ https://github.com/bellhyve/zelta/issues
**************************************************************************
